# {{ project_name }}

SvelteKit + TypeScript project scaffolded with [skap](https://github.com/skap-cli/skap).
Runs on port `{{ app_port }}` with hot reload.

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.example .env
skap start {{ project_name }}
```

Then open <http://localhost:{{ app_port }}>.

## Useful commands

```bash
skap logs  {{ project_name }}
skap shell {{ project_name }}
skap run   {{ project_name }} npm run check
skap stop  {{ project_name }}
```

